div.p: Power-On BIOS Stage1 (0x7C00) A20 Stage2 GDT Protected Mode kernel_main

p.strong: Key Failure Modes Triple Fault Causes

ul.li: Boot sig wrong: BIOS skips device
lgdt before cli: IVT dispatch in PM #GP #DF triple
No far jmp after CR0.PE: pipeline inconsistency #GP
DF=1 before rep stosb: BSS zero runs backward
BSS not zeroed: global vars = garbage undefined behavior
ESP unmapped: first push triple fault

text.tspan: CR0.PE must be 0 at this point
; CPU IS NOW IN PROTECTED MODE
cld ; DF=0 FIRST (req for rep stosb)
; C ABI: DF must be 0 on entry
; BIOS may have left DF=1 corruption
; No IDT yet any exception = triple fault
